CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 10, 1959, pg. 13 reads: "Mr. And Mrs. James Norman Schofield - Mary Boyce Hutson became the bride of James Norman Schofield in pretty rites performed Dec. 20 in family home on Magee St. The pre-holiday ritual was attended by family and close friends. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Groom James Norman Schofield, and bride Mary Boyce Hutson, posing in home on Magee Street with bold print wallpaper of ivy frames and polka dots
